{"tid":860090,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[人人生而平等] 貨幣匯率係邊個定㗎？","createTime":"2018-10-13T05:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T07:09:03.000Z","uid":125976,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8624578c51fddff4ddd5ff2efaeb14252c1cde86","tid":860090,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:28:19.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好想問依條問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解喺挪威洗大餅會高人工過一個喺印度嘅專業工程師？<br />\n<br />\n公平咩？公平咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然你可以話喺挪威賺得多洗得多，喺印度你做工程師每個月揸住幾千蚊港紙都食得好住得好。<br />\n<br />\n但問題係價值始終係價值，咁喺挪威做嘢始終搵得多過印度佬幾倍就係唔公平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋挪威佬有手有腳可以走，佢可賺挪威錢喺印度、泰國洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好以為依樣嘢唔關香港事。<br />\n<br />\n正如同樣資歷經驗嘅 IT 狗，喺美國 fresh grad 已經每個月至少六七皮港紙，入到 Facebook, Google 分鐘十二三萬一個月。但你喺香港每個月有兩三皮已經算好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa8ba2266c69713b40a37358fbb6b43449acc786","tid":860090,"uid":191041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"邊個話你知人係平等 你比人洗咗腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cce8c0d121e899b73cbb4a32d0261dc726fcb9","tid":860090,"uid":125976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa8ba2266c69713b40a37358fbb6b43449acc786","tid":860090,"uid":191041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:51:29.000Z","msg":"邊個話你知人係平等 你比人洗咗腦啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:52:45.000Z","msg":"反諷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e229d64acbc1720e3ef6f1e700121af42a67cf58","tid":860090,"uid":55614,"lik